      <title>首席经济学家莱恩表示，欧洲央行降息的理由越来越充分</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/ecb-rate-cut-case-getting-stronger-says-chief-economist-lane-2024-05-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行首席经济学家 Philip Lane 周一对西班牙报纸《机密报》表示，随着服务业通胀终于开始缓解，欧洲央行 6 月份降息的理由越来越充分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/ecb-rate-cut-case-getting-stronger-says-chief-economist-lane-2024-05-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 03:06:24 GMT</pubDate>
